UnitUniswapV2CollateralAdapter::constructor
└── when deployed
    ├── it sets LP_TOKEN
    └── it sets VAULT_MANAGER


UnitUniswapV2CollateralAdapter::deposit
├── when called by a non-vaultManager
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by the vaultManager
    ├── it transfers LP tokens from the user to the adapter
    └── it emits Deposited


UnitUniswapV2CollateralAdapter::withdraw
├── when called by a non-vaultManager
│   └── it reverts
└── when called by the vaultManager
    ├── it transfers LP tokens to the recipient
    └── it emits Withdrawn


UnitUniswapV2CollateralAdapter::adapterBalance
└── when called
    └── it returns the LP token balance held by the adapter


UnitUniswapV2CollateralAdapter::pair
└── when called
    └── it returns the pair interface for LP_TOKEN
